rows.label: tlk42100121_01_msg0001
rows.name:
Takaka loves high places, mo! It
took a whole year of hard work to
finally climb up on this roof, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100121_01_msg0002
rows.name:
Takaka's goal is to climb to the
very top of that windmill, mo!

rows.label: tlk42100121_01_msg0003
rows.name:
But Takaka still hasn't figured
out how to climb it... mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_01_msg0004
rows.name:
At times like this, Drivers have it good,
mo. Being able to use a Blade's power to
jump to high places is so enviable, mo.

rows.label: tlk42100121_01_msg0005
rows.name: Takaka wants to be a Driver too... mo.
